name: "cathy" deformed bear collection
description: meet "cathy" a lover of breakfast and slurpees. hates long walks but loves a good game of table tennis. do not leave Cathy unattended during meal time. Good luck.  Selling my friends and their personalities. Warping my childhood memories one bear at a time. hope you enjoy. (i will save you from the mediocrity and the confused. i will breast feed you back to life. you will be raise as one of my own. there will come a time when you will be sacrificed solely for the amusement of the devils. but your bones will live forever.... that is my promise)  "I AM PUGS" - DEFORMED.
